enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve manipulating the enforcedAttributes map, making addEnforcedAttribute a natural setup for removeEnforcedAttribute.
getEnforcedAttributes retrieves the enforced attributes for a tag, which can be useful to verify the state before and after calling removeEnforcedAttribute.
isSafeAttribute checks if an attribute is safe for a tag, which can be used to verify the safety of attributes after removing an enforced attribute.
